Lucie and Craig have found
this kind of love,

1:19:52.088 --> 1:19:53.821
and we should all be
so lucky,

1:19:53.856 --> 1:19:58.392
so let's raise our glasses
to Lucie and Craig,

1:19:58.427 --> 1:20:02.396
may you have a beautiful
life together.

